import React from 'react'
import { FaSearch } from "react-icons/fa";

const Search = () => {
    return (
        <from>
            <input
                type="text"
                className="from-control"
                placeholder="Search"
            >
            </input>
            <button>
                <FaSearch />
            </button>
        </from>
    )
}

export default Search
